# UI Design Guidelines for 悦伴

## Design Principles
1. **Magazine Layout**: Large images, minimal dividers, visual impact
2. **Natural & Healing**: Forest breath aesthetic, calm and professional
3. **Micro-interactions**: Subtle animations enhance immersion
4. **Consistency**: Unified design system across all screens

## Color System
Use colors from `lib/utils/constants.dart`:

```dart
// Primary Colors
static const Color primaryColor = Color(0xFF1A3C34);      // Deep Pine
static const Color secondaryColor = Color(0xFFF2F0EB);    // Warm Stone
static const Color accentColor = Color(0xFFD97D54);       // Ember Orange
static const Color neutralColor = Color(0xFF333333);      // Basalt Grey

// Supporting Colors
static const Color softGray = Color(0xFFE5E7EB);
static const Color white = Colors.white;
static const Color black = Colors.black;
```

## 60-30-10 Color Rule
- **60%** Background (Warm Stone #F2F0EB, White)
- **30%** Brand elements (Deep Pine #1A3C34) - Nav, headers, titles
- **10%** Accents (Ember Orange #D97D54) - CTAs, highlights, badges

