## Bottom Navigation
- Height: 88px (including safe area)
- Icons: 20-24px
- Label: 10px
- Active color: primaryColor
- Inactive color: grey[400]
- Center FAB: accentColor, 48px diameter

## Status Bar
- Semi-transparent background
- Height: 48px + safe area top
- Time left, notch center, icons right
- Adapt text color based on background

## Loading States
```dart
// Shimmer effect or simple progress
Center(
  child: CircularProgressIndicator(
    valueColor: AlwaysStoppedAnimation<Color>(primaryColor),
  ),
)
```

## Empty States
- Large icon (48-64px)
- Descriptive text
- Optional CTA button
- Center aligned

## Animation Guidelines
- Duration: 200-300ms for most interactions
- Curves: Use `Curves.easeInOut` for smooth transitions
- Avoid excessive animations
- Add haptic feedback for important actions

## Accessibility
- Ensure text contrast ratio ≥ 4.5:1
- Minimum touch target: 44x44px
- Provide semantic labels for icons
- Support dynamic text sizing
